LINE.Text: The United Nations Multidimensional Integrated Stabilization Mission in Mali (MINUSMA) was
established on 25 April 2013 to support political processes and carry out a number of security-related
tasks However, since its launch on 1 July 2013 peacekeepers have been victims of various
types of attacks, including ambush, suicide bombings, shelling, indirect fire and IEDs.
